# Privacy Policy for Little Kingdom

**Effective Date:** March 22, 2026

Little Kingdom ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting the privacy of children and families who use our application.

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our game.

---

## 👶 Children’s Privacy

Little Kingdom is designed for children and families. We take children's privacy seriously and comply with applicable laws including the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA).

We do **not knowingly collect personally identifiable information** from children under the age of 13.

If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us so we can remove it promptly.

---

## 📊 Information We Collect

We may collect limited non-personal information to improve the experience, including:

* Device type and operating system
* Gameplay progress and interactions
* App performance data (crashes, errors)

We do **not collect**:

* Names
* Addresses
* Phone numbers
* Exact location data

---

## 🎮 How We Use Information

We use collected data to:

* Improve gameplay experience
* Fix bugs and performance issues
* Enhance educational content
* Ensure app stability and safety

---

## 🤖 AI Features

If AI-powered features are used, they are designed to:

* Provide educational responses
* Support scripture-based learning
* Enhance gameplay interaction

AI does **not store personal user data**.

---

## 🔒 Data Security

We implement reasonable safeguards to protect information and ensure a safe environment for all users.

---

## 🌍 Third-Party Services

We may use trusted third-party services (such as hosting or analytics providers) that help operate the app. These services are required to maintain privacy and security standards.

---

## 🚫 Advertising

Little Kingdom is designed to be a safe, ad-free experience for children.

We do **not display third-party advertisements**.

---

## 🛑 Parental Rights

Parents and guardians have the right to:

* Request deletion of any data
* Ask questions about data usage
* Control their child’s interaction with the app

---

## 🔄 Updates to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Changes will be reflected with a new effective date.

